To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private StalledPattern _stalledpattern;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_stalledpattern = StalledPattern(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_stalledpattern.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "stalledpattern", _stalledpattern.Current.Value);
}
